ZH: 我们去舞厅跳舞。
EN: We went to the dance hall to dance.

ZH: 在舞厅里音乐很吵。
EN: The music was very loud in the dance hall.

ZH: 他们在舞厅里举行了一个舞会。
EN: They held a dance party in the dance hall.

ZH: 我们在舞厅里见到了很多人。
EN: We saw a lot of people in the dance hall.

ZH: 这家酒店有一个很大的舞厅。
EN: This hotel has a very big dance hall.

ZH: 今晚我们去舞厅跳舞。
EN: Tonight we are going to the dance hall to dance.

ZH: 周末的时候，舞厅总是很热闹。
EN: The dance hall is always lively on weekends.

ZH: 我们在舞厅里学习了很多舞蹈。
EN: We learned a lot of dances in the dance hall.

ZH: 在舞厅里跳舞能锻炼身体。
EN: Dancing in the dance hall is good exercise.

ZH: 他们在舞厅里玩得很开心。
EN: They had a great time in the dance hall.

ZH: 每个周末，我们都会去舞厅跳舞。
EN: Every weekend, we go to the dance hall to dance.

ZH: 舞厅里的灯光很漂亮。
EN: The lights in the dance hall are very pretty.

ZH: 我在舞厅里遇到了我的朋友。
EN: I met my friend in the dance hall.

ZH: 我的姐妹在舞厅里跳舞跳得很好。
EN: My sister dances very well in the dance hall.

ZH: 在舞厅里跳舞使人心情愉快。
EN: Dancing in the dance hall brings joy to people.

ZH: 舞厅里的音乐声震耳欲聋。
EN: The music in the dance hall is deafening.

ZH: 我们在舞厅里练习舞蹈。
EN: We practice dancing in the dance hall.

ZH: 舞厅里的气氛很欢乐。
EN: The atmosphere in the dance hall is festive.

ZH: 在舞厅里跳舞让人忘记烦恼。
EN: Dancing in the dance hall helps people forget their troubles.

ZH: 他们在舞厅里表演了一场精彩的舞蹈。
EN: They performed a wonderful dance in the dance hall.
